                  </hi>. Aged 28.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prisoner was further charged with having been before convicted: to which he pleaded guilty</hi>.)</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Henry Webb and John Mark Bull, of the City police, and Inspector Brannan, of the G division, deposed to the prisoner having been convicted several times, to his being a trainer of young thieves, and getting his living by thieving</hi>.)</p>
